description:
MuscleTech Platinum 100% Omega Fish Oil

MuscleTech Platinum 100% Omega Fish Oil uses only the most ultra-pure filtered fish oil to supply the key omega-3 fatty acids in fish oil docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) and eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) Platinum 100% Omega Fish Oil soft gels give your body the EPA and DHA it needs to be it is very best.

The soft coated gel prevents the fishy aftertaste which you can get with lower quality fish oil products. It’s perfect for a stack with other Muscletech essential series products.

No Fishy Aftertaste

An enteric coating on the delicate soft gels prevents premature breakdown and helps you avoid the fishy aftertaste or bothersome fish burps you may get with lower quality fish oil products!

‡ MuscleTech is America’s #1 Selling Bodybuilding Supplement Brand based on cumulative wholesale dollar sales 2001 to present.

Benefits of Consuming Fish Oil Supplements : 

  • Better Immunity & Stamina: Say bye to frequent cough and cold with a daily dose of fish oil capsule in your diet. Fish oil has anti-inflammatory properties that help in reducing inflammation in the body and therefore increases the body immunity to fight off infections and injuries.
  • Improves Vision &  Brain Health: Fish oil is a powerful antioxidant that prevents any free radical damage to the brain cells and improving cognitive function.
  • Healthy Hair and Skin: Fish oil capsules make for a rich source of antioxidants in the body , and therefore, prevent issues like skin ageing, dryness & brittle hair. It revives dry scalp and fights split ends.

Suggested Use

Take 1 serving (1 capsule) daily with a glass of water. Do not exceed 1 capsule in a 24-hour period. Read the entire label before use and follow directions provided.

short_description:
GNC Amp Gold BCAA Advanced Series contains7g of Instantized BCAA in optimal 2:1:1 ratio– 3.5g Leucine, 1.75g Iso-Leucine & 1.75g Valine.

It also contains 1g of L-citrulline (precursor of arginine) for better muscle strength & 1g of L-glutamine to improve recovery and immunity. Its a versatile sports drink for both pre- and post-workout.

The three amino acids function alone or as a group to trigger protein production for muscle growth and repair along with three important nutrients:

· Leucine stimulates muscle growth and strength. It regulates blood sugar before and after exercise.

· Valine prevents muscle breakdown during exercise and supports muscle metabolism and growth.

· Isoleucine helps with energy production and increases nitrogen growth in muscle cells.

· L-Citrulline can be recycled to arginine in the citrulline-NO cycle, in turn contributing to nitric oxide production.

· Glutamine plays an important role in muscle function during and after exercise.

· Vitamin B6 being the water soluble vitamin gets lost in sweat during strenuous exercise and training.

Benefits

1. Better Muscle Strength

2. Prevents Muscle Breakdown during intensive workout

3. Improves Recovery Time and Immunity

4. Caffeine & Creatine Free
